>Jesse: EGGKQSZ -GGKQ +0 376
#note oof, another tough play. I decided that I have to exchange because I have no plan for dumping the Q, and no chance of outrunning any bingo with GGKQ all to play through. I decided to keep the Z because I'm only one tile away from 50+ point Z plays, and it gives me potentially huge responses to Akshay's bingos. but I think it would also be reasonable to exchange the Z and try to draw a bingo, and hope that the GGKQZ mess prove even more crippling to Akshay than just GGKQ alone. *shrug*
